      "name": null,
      "patch_url": null
    },
    "body": "The connman fuzz harness never sets `fSuccessfullyConnected=true` on nodes added through `AddTestNode()`. `NodeFullyConnected()` gates `ForEachNode()` on that flag, making its callback unreachable in the current harness.\r\nSet `fSuccessfullyConnected=true` before `AddTestNode()` to simulate a node that has completed the version handshake. ",
